---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me" description="Learn more about me and my journey into web development.">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-9">About This Blog</h1>

  <div class="format dark:format-invert max-w-none">
    <p>
      Welcome! This blog is a space dedicated to sharing my thoughts, experiences, and learnings about web development,
      with a particular focus on modern JavaScript frameworks like Astro.js, and front-end technologies such as Tailwind
      CSS.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">My Journey</h2>

    <p>
      My journey into the world of web development began several years ago. I've always been fascinated by the power of
      the internet and the ability to create interactive and engaging experiences for users. Starting with the basics of
      HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, I gradually expanded my skills to include more advanced frameworks and tools.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">What You'll Find Here</h2>

    <p>On this blog, you'll find a variety of content related to web development, including:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
      <li>
        <strong>Tutorials:</strong> Step-by-step guides on implementing specific features or solving common problems.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Articles:</strong> In-depth explorations of various web development topics.</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Code Examples:</strong> Practical examples demonstrating how to use different technologies and frameworks.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Personal Reflections:</strong> My thoughts and experiences on the challenges and rewards of being a web developer.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">My Skills</h2>

    <p>I have experience with the following technologies:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
      <li><strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, HTML, CSS</li>
      <li><strong>Frameworks:</strong> Astro, React, Vue.js, Tailwind CSS, Node.js</li>
      <li><strong>Tools:</strong> Git, Webpack, npm, VS Code</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">Let's Connect!</h2>

    <p>
      I'm always open to connecting with other developers and sharing knowledge. Feel free to reach out to me via the
      contact form or on social media.
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for visiting!</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
